<asp:Content ID="BodyContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="MainContent" runat="server">
    <h2 class="text-primary"><%: Title %></h2>
    <h3>Smart Neightborhood Web Application.</h3>
    <p>Smart Neighborhood web application is designed for homeowner associations (HOAs) to use within their communities. This web application is intended to streamline the communication flow between homeowners and the HOA and provide users with relevant information about their community. It will facilitate routine management tasks such as billing, payments, and reporting of HOA violations. The HOAs will be responsible for establishing network connectivity and managing the services.  For each house within the HOA community, the HOA will install a Smart Neighborhood Application. HOA’s may choose to deploy this application to touchscreens in houses for ease of use and to encourage daily use.</p>

</asp:Content>
